						<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://docserver.scripting.com/drummer/electricDrummer.opml#1634740239000&quot;&gt;Doesn't Electron suck&lt;/a&gt;?" created="Wed, 20 Oct 2021 14:34:26 GMT"/>
						</outline>
					<outline text="I changed the name of the &lt;a href=&quot;http://docserver.scripting.com/drummer/general.opml&quot;&gt;General page&lt;/a&gt; to FAQs. " created="Wed, 20 Oct 2021 14:49:45 GMT"/>
					<outline text="Many of the docs I'm grabbing from the Change notes outline are going into that (new) page. " created="Wed, 20 Oct 2021 16:42:59 GMT"/>
					<outline text="Everything on this page is rough, needs a review, which I plan to do when I get a fresh perspective.  " created="Wed, 20 Oct 2021 16:43:06 GMT"/>
					<outline text="BTW, the one feature you all may not know about is Drag and Drop outlines in Drummer. I added it to the &lt;a href=&quot;http://docserver.scripting.com/drummer/files.opml#1634743285000&quot;&gt;Files&lt;/a&gt; page. There's a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FKM65EL6abo&quot;&gt;video demo&lt;/a&gt;." created="Wed, 20 Oct 2021 15:34:06 GMT"/>
					<outline text="I have one more big item on my docs list for today -- documenting the head-level atts for blogging. " created="Wed, 20 Oct 2021 15:35:35 GMT"/>
