					</outline>
				<outline text="Home page for oldschool.scripting.com" created="Sat, 16 Oct 2021 13:42:09 GMT" type="outline">
					<outline text="There was no index page for the site. I put a &lt;a href=&quot;http://oldschool.scripting.com/&quot;&gt;placeholder&lt;/a&gt; there. " created="Sat, 16 Oct 2021 13:44:28 GMT"/>
